platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Duolingo is one of the most successful language-learning apps in the world. Now with Duolingo ABC, kids ages 3 to 6 can get in on the fun with English reading activities. Packed with games and engaging exercises, Duolingo ABC applies the same tried and true methods that make Duolingo so popularonly with a lot more cute monkeys.
Taking tried-and-true methods from its parent app Duolingo, this is made for kids aged 3 to 6 and is packed with English-language games and engaging exercises  and a lot of cute monkeys.
